OL,3,CPolice officer found dead in Bristol
OL,4,Charbour believed to have drowned
OL,6,FA police officer is believed to have
OL,7,Fdrowned in a harbour after going
OL,8,Fmissing during a night out, an inquest
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FPC Rehaan Akhtar, 28, had been
OL,12,Fdrinking with friends in Bristol and
OL,13,Fwas last seen in the early hours of 23
OL,14,FNovember.
OL,16,FHe did not return to the hostel where
OL,17,Fhe was staying and was reported
OL,18,Fmissing, Avon Coroner's Court heard.
