OL,3,CPolice officer found dead in Bristol
OL,4,Charbour believed to have drowned
OL,6,FHis body was recovered by divers from
OL,7,FBristol harbourside on the morning of
OL,8,F24 November.
OL,10,FMr Akhtar, from Llanelli, was a
OL,11,Fconstable with South Wales Police.
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination took place
OL,14,Fand the provisional cause of PC
OL,15,FAkhtar's death was recorded as
OL,16,Fdrowning.
OL,18,FDebbie Rookes, assistant coroner for
OL,19,FAvon, opened and adjourned an inquest
OL,20,Finto PC Akhtar's death on Wednesday, 3
OL,21,FDecember.
