OL,6,FMrs Rookes provisionally listed the
OL,7,Finquest for a hearing on 24 February
OL,8,F2026.
OL,10,FMr Akhtar was a PCSO in Cardiff from
OL,11,FOctober 2021 and became a PC based in
OL,12,FSwansea in September 2023.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Chief Constable Jeremy
OL,15,FVaughan of South Wales Police said: "I
OL,16,Fwas shocked and saddened to learn of
OL,17,FRehaan's passing.
