OL,6,F"At this difficult time, our hearts go
OL,7,Fout to Rehaan's family and friends,
OL,8,Fand we will do all we can to support
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"During his time with South Wales
OL,12,FPolice he served our communities with
OL,13,Fpride and professionalism as both a
OL,14,FPCSO and a police officer.
OL,16,F"I know he was greatly respected and
OL,17,Fliked by his colleagues and those he
OL,18,Fmet as part of his day-to-day duties.
